hort for Voronezh Semiconductor Devices Plant, in Voronezh, capital of the Russian  Voronezh Oblast. The attack hit during normal working hours, killing 5 people and wounding several dozen more according to the regional governor: https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/five-dead-after-attack-russias-voronezh-governor-says-2026-06-22/

The plant produced electronic components critical for various Russian missile systems that are being used in Russia's war against Ukraine, e.g. the Kh-101 cruise missile (used in an attack on the Okhmatdyt children's hospital in Kyiv), the 9K720 Iskander (responsible for the first Ukrainian losses of HIMARS and Patriot) and Pantsir anti-air missile systems (the backbone of Russia's missile-based air-defense against Ukrainian drones and cruise missiles): https://en.defence-ua.com/news/what_did_vzpp_plant_in_voronezh_do_before_ukrainian_cruise_missiles_hit_it_and_why_does_it_matter_for_kh_101_r_500-18899.html

While Ukrainian press and Russian military official sources suggest that the weapon systems used in this attack were Storm Shadow cruise missiles, supplied to Ukraine by the UK and France, independent military analysts have pointed out that characteristics visible in the available video footage fit better to AGM-188 Rusty Dagger air-launched cruise missiles, a brand-new cruise missile by Zone 5 Technologies (of Norwegian company Kongsberg Gruppen) produced for the US Air Force. Zone 5 Technologies revealed in early June 2026 that Rusty Daggers, capable of being launched by F-16, have been supplied to Ukraine for field-testing: https://www.twz.com/air/kongsberg-bets-on-high-low-cruise-missile-mix-with-jsm-and-rusty-dagger</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w05vhRG.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>To add insult to injury: OSINT analysts identified Russian air defense as the cause of the now famous explosion at Moscow's oil refinery: https://theins.press/en/news/293893</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gKeJ677.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Please consider donating to Ukraine using the official government website: https://u24.gov.ua/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/aRgLdg5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DerpMeister]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Looks the same to me</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SmaQ2qy</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EuG0Vqf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SmaQ2qy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Pasquinelthe2nd]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>No sir, you stay on that fiction shelf</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5SJYQ9l</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/duJ9crP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5SJYQ9l</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[svardfiska]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>VJayBombs – Projections in DC on the tarp covering the area where Trump's name was removed from the Kennedy Center – "No-one Bends The Knee Like The GOP"</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VBogUc2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ncKZOzh.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VBogUc2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OceansRust]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Disabled American's may no longer have homes...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/6OSIBhD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EXTLc5w.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e0BLBBf.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LgUbbhY.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://x.com/theaisbarks/status/2069205038661042616?s=46

https://www.npr.org/2026/06/20/nx-s1-5865100/doj-memo-trump-disability-civil-rights-institutionalization

https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/new-justice-department-memo-questions-decades-of-protections-for-people-with-disabilities

From Twitter https://x.com/Gianl1974/status/2069087162528624820
A Justice Department lawyer just signed a memo saying disabled Americans have no right to live in their own homes. In the same document, she admits no court in the country agrees with her.

Read that again. A government official wrote down, in black and white, that her own argument is wrong by every legal standard of the last thirty years, and she made it anyway.

Here is what it means in plain terms.

Right now, 8.4 million people get help that lets them stay in their own homes. Aides who help them dress. Care that lets them work, see friends, raise their kids, sleep in their own beds at night.

This memo tells states they can cut all of it.

And if they cut it, where do those people go? Into nursing homes. Into institutions. Into facilities where someone else decides when you wake up, what you eat, who your roommate is, whether you go outside today.

A lawyer who has visited people locked in these places said their whole world shrinks to one hallway. That is the future this memo is opening the door to.

Keeping people in their own homes is cheaper. In one case, home care cost under $7,500 a year. The nursing home would have cost close to $50,000. The cruel option is also the expensive one. They want to spend more money to make people's lives worse.

So why?

Because last summer Trump signed an order to deal with homelessness by force, by sweeping people off the streets and committing them. He said it out loud during the campaign: the mentally ill belong back in institutions.

The only thing standing in the way was the law that says people deserve to live in their own communities.

This memo is how they get around it. And it landed the same week Republicans slashed Medicaid, giving every cash-strapped state the perfect excuse to start cutting.

A think tank drew up the plan. A lawyer wrote the memo. A president signed the order. Three signatures, and millions of people could lose the right to their own front door.

We are about to spend the summer celebrating 250 years of American freedom.
Some Americans are about to find out it doesn't include them.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6OSIBhD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Imadethisaccounttopost]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Getting corrected by a Japanese mom</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/F5wENMz</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EZotP74.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/F5wENMz</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Huor]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Always Was and Still Is</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UvnS0LY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3G4Sx2q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UvnS0LY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Resistance1000]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Reason to ponder</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/S7f2QAK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YUORShs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/S7f2QAK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KatLuvr54]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Removing these from my phone part 37</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mcXmpaP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JHCfCBa.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cfHRtT6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/s0i6DAu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/m4ldikP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cwNNaJe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><